     C                     MOVE AKFLG     PKFLG
     C                     EXSR SAT                        *
     C                     EXSR SUBJOB                     HD WRITE LOG
     C                     EXCPTDAT                        *
     C                     MOVE '*'       PSFLG
     C                     GOTO STPEND                     *
